  <brief_title>Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of Scarclinic™ Thin in Surgical Scars</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study of Scarclinic™ Thin That Treats Surgical Scars.</official_title>
